  "texts": [
    "Leveraging channel and sensor imperfections, machine learning models can identify transient and steady-state parameters to authenticate sensors and ensure secure communication.By incorporating AI technologies into user and device authentication processes, organizations can bolster their protective measures and proactively secure their systems against unauthorized access and potential threats DetectThe detect function is responsible for promptly identifying cybersecurity events through the implementation of appropriate activities.",
    "Its primary objective is to minimize disruption by ensuring timely discovery.",
    "This function encompasses activities such as intrusion and anomaly detection, impact assessment, continuous security monitoring, and maintaining effective detection processes to stay aware of cyber events.",
    "AI technology can significantly improve detection speed by monitoring internal and external information sources and rapidly correlating data to identify unusual activities, thus minimizing the potential consequences.• Intrusion detection and response-Intrusion detection systems (IDS) and intrusion response systems (IRS) are pivotal in detecting and responding to computer system intrusions.",
    "Leveraging AI and machine learning (ML), IDS and IRS systems have become adept at identifying new threats and adapting to evolving attack patterns."
  ]
